CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 7, 2014

[Cite as 03/07/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-847.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2014-0276. State v. C.K.

Cuyahoga App. No. 99886, 2013-Ohio-5135. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal.

Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to file the case under seal, it is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
